    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is recommended for those looking for a major project or a source for parts. The exterior has significant rust, several large dents, and the paint is peeling across most surfaces. Mechanically, the engine requires a complete overhaul, and the transmission is currently slipping; it is not in drivable condition. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with several tears, and the electronics are largely non-functional. It will need to be towed from its current location.",
