    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies consistent care and mechanical integrity. This unit offers a refined driving experience, featuring a clean interior and a robust powertrain that has undergone a rigorous professional inspection. Ideal for the discerning driver seeking a balance of performance and proven reliability, this vehicle stands as a testament to quality engineering and remains in commendable condition for its next owner.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Looking for a reliable ride that still looks and feels great? I\u2019m selling my car and it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in solid, dependable shape and has been really well-loved over the years. Whether you're just commuting to work or heading out on a weekend road trip, this beauty is ready to go! Honestly, it drives like a dream and I'd love to see it go to a good home. Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel for a test drive!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 naturally aspirated inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and high-pressure dual VANOS variable valve timing. Mated to a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, the drivetrain sends power to the rear wheels via a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis remains composed thanks to proactive subframe reinforcement and refreshed bushings. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive valve clearance adjustment and cooling system overhaul, ensuring the high-revving internals remain within factory tolerances. A driver-focused machine offering exceptional mechanical feedback and a rigid, well-balanced platform.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Used vehicle. Good condition. Regular maintenance performed. Clean title. Minimal wear. Engine runs strong.",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a well-maintained vehicle that balances performance with everyday utility. The exterior finish remains vibrant and glossy, though it shows light evidence of its time on the road with a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger-side wheel arch. The alloy wheels are wrapped in premium tires with approximately 70% tread remaining. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free; the bolsters on the driver\u2019s seat show very slight wear, but the leather remains soft and free of punctures. All interior technology, including the navigation system, backup camera, and heated seats, operates exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is robust. It has a documented service history, with the most recent oil change and brake pad replacement performed just 1,500 miles ago. The engine idles smoothly, and the transmission shifts crisply through all gears. This is a dependable, honest example of a car that has been cared for by an enthusiast. Includes two sets of keys and the original owner\u2019s manuals.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this impeccably maintained vehicle, which serves as a testament to disciplined ownership and engineering longevity. This specimen boasts a robust service history and has passed a comprehensive multi-point inspection, ensuring that its mechanical systems operate with precision. The exterior retains a sophisticated luster, while the interior cabin remains a refined environment for both driver and passengers. This offering represents an exceptional opportunity for the discerning buyer seeking a reliable, high-caliber vehicle that balances performance with enduring value.",
      "price": 33800.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s honestly been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. Whether you're commuting or heading out on a road trip, this car is ready to go and looking for a great new home. Come take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re going to love how it handles!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock for superior mechanical grip. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rod bearing replacement and a comprehensive rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural integrity under lateral load. The suspension geometry remains tight, providing the communicative feedback and balanced weight distribution this chassis is renowned for. A true driver\u2019s example with a clear emphasis on mechanical health and powertrain response.",
